Package ru.nsu.vyaznikova

Class AdjacencyMatrix<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nsu.vyaznikova.AbstractGraph<T>
      • ru.nsu.vyaznikova.AdjacencyMatrix<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the vertices in the graph.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph<T>
    public class AdjacencyMatrix<T>
extends AbstractGraph<T>
    Represents a graph using an adjacency matrix data structure with a growing array. The graph can handle vertices of any type using generics.

      • readFromFile

        public void readFromFile​(java.lang.String filename)
        Reads the graph from a file. The file format is as follows:
        First line: number of vertices N.
        Next N lines: vertex names (strings).
        Remaining lines: edges, where each line contains a pair of vertices separated by space (e.g., A B).
